node.text: A vacation I will never, ever forget. Truthfully, I never understood the hype or how adults could be so obsessed with Disney, but, wow, now it ALL makes sense! I truly cannot wait to come back here. We smiled the biggest smiles, walked for miles, continuously talked about how amazed we were, Remi lost a tooth, we did a gender reveal for my sister, we stayed up late talking about our days, and made memories that we’ll remember for a lifetime! Disney truly is MAGICAL.✨ // Looking ahead, we have some big things happening in the upcoming months. The kids start school next week, I have some work ventures and product launches that I can’t WAIT to share, and we are going to start working on getting the Arkansas house ready for y’all to stay.❤️ // Love y’all, friends! Thanks you for coming along with us to Disney in Stories this week!🥰 #disneyworld #iloveyou

node.text: You know it’s a good day when Kyle agrees to wear matching shirts!😁 First day at Disney parks did not disappoint. We’re already in our pajamas resting up for day 2! Well, the parents are in pajamas, the kids are still wired up!😂 Do you have Disney favorites? Rides, food, anything? Let us know; we love seeing y’all’s recommendations.🥰 xo! #disneyworld #makingeveryonewearmatchingshirts
